                >Staff</span
              >
              <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">Nov 7, 2025 at 10:45 AM</span>
            </div>
            <div
              class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-100 rounded-2xl rounded-tl-none p-4"
            >
              <p class="text-gray-900">
                Hello! Thank you for reaching out. I apologize for the
